Package edu.asu.itunesu

Interface Summary
SectionItem A Division or Group contained within a Section.
 

Class Summary
Course A collection of Group objects.
Division A collection of Section objects.
ExternalFeed An external RSS feed for a Group.
Group A collection of Track objects, viewable as a tab.
ITunesUConnection The iTunesU Web Services API connection.
ITunesUDocument Used internally to construct XML requests.
ITunesUElement Abstract base class for all elements in an iTunesU site.
ITunesUResponse A response from an iTunesU Web Services API call.
Permission A permission record containing credential and access settings.
Section A collection of SectionItem objects.
Site An entire iTunesU site, composed of many Section objects.
Templates A collection of default values for an iTunesU site.
Track A multimedia document.
 

Exception Summary
ITunesUException iTunesU exception class.
